text: Gabrijela Bešen (born 6 December 1994) is a Croatian handball player for MKS Selgros Lublin and the Croatian national team. She participated at the 2016 European Women's Handball Championship.2016 European Championship roster ==References== == External links == * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian female handball players
